# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PATIENT DATA PROTECTION — TOP PRIORITY
# Any file containing real patient records must NEVER appear in this repository.
# Rules below provide defence-in-depth: file extension, filename pattern, and
# directory-level blocks all work independently.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Spreadsheet / database file extensions (any name, any directory) ──────────
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.xlsm
*.xlsb
*.csv
*.tsv
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.mdb
*.accdb
*.sav          # SPSS data files
*.sas7bdat     # SAS data files
*.dta          # Stata data files

# Allow synthetic test fixtures ONLY (must be generated, never real data)
!tests/fixtures/*.xlsx

# ── Name-pattern blocks — catch common registry output filenames ───────────────
decoded_*
Clinical_Clean*
Reverse_Verification*
All_Fields_Decoded*
*cancer_registry*
*registry_data*
*患者*
*病人*
*個案*

# ── Explicit sensitive content patterns ───────────────────────────────────────
*metaplastic*
*patient_data*
*patient_info*
*real_data*
*PHI*
*PII*
*identified*
*de-identified*
*deidentified*
*anonymized*

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Python
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
.eggs/

# ── Virtual environments ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.venv/
venv/
env/
.env

# ── Test & coverage ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
coverage.xml

# ── IDE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# ── OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── Log and cache files ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.txt
*_cache.json
decode_log.txt
final_log.txt
general_decode_log.txt
inspect_log.txt
llm_decode_log.txt
vision_decode_log.txt

# ── Large reference files (use Git LFS if needed) ─────────────────────────────
pdf_chunks/
codebook_md/

# ── Archive of superseded scripts ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Entire directory blocked — contains real data files from development phase
_archive/
